<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Join the Club · Members Only</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="sheet">
      <header class="masthead">
        <p class="title">Members Only</p>
        <p class="tagline">Talk is cheap. Membership isn't.</p>
      </header>

      <h1>The secret handshake</h1>
      <p>
        There's no fee — just a question every member is expected to know.
        Answer it and you're one of us.
      </p>

      <form action="/jointheclub" method="POST">
        <label for="password">Which fish costs the most?</label>
        <input id="password" name="password" type="password" required />

        <button type="submit">Say the word</button>
      </form>

      <hr />
      <p class="muted"><a href="/">Back to the board</a></p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>